  <brief_title>Influence of Bag Volume Variation on the Reproducibility of Inert Gas Rebreathing</brief_title>
  <official_title>Influence of Bag Volume Variation in Inert Gas Rebreathing Pulmonary Blood Flow Measurements on the Reproducibility in Patients With Pulmonary Diseases</official_title>
